he has a chance to kill you, or would you

00:03:01.960 --> 00:03:05.690
rather be able to outrun them, no matter where
they are.

00:03:05.690 --> 00:03:09.170
This bring me to my next point, buy boots.

00:03:09.170 --> 00:03:11.049
Buy several pairs of boots.

00:03:11.049 --> 00:03:12.700
The more the merrier.

00:03:12.700 --> 00:03:16.780
If you do not have 3 pairs of boots by the
five minute mark, then you need to go back

00:03:16.780 --> 00:03:17.780
